+// DisplayXR inline-3D (#625, Step B / B4): bind the renderer's per-frame
+// DisplayXRService to the browser-process weave client's cached state. Dormant
+// unless --enable-inline-3d — dropping the receiver makes the renderer's remote
+// disconnect, so isSessionSupported('inline-3d') resolves false (negative
+// control). Mirrors content/shell's BindDisplayXRService.
+void BindDisplayXRService(
+    content::RenderFrameHost* render_frame_host,
